<item>
            <title>[WICKET-5893] CookieUtils should use the original response when saving a cookie</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5893</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Report at users@: &lt;a href=&quot;http://markmail.org/message/7ep5kar6kvmn766l&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://markmail.org/message/7ep5kar6kvmn766l&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

