&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5893&quot; title=&quot;CookieUtils should use the original response when saving a cookie&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-5893&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-5893&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; CookieUtils should use the original response when saving a cookie&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fallback to the original response only if the current one is not WebResponse. This way the buffering (BufferedWebResponse) is preserved if possible&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
