[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=wicket.git;h=b88977e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=wicket.git;h=b88977e&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5893&quot; title=&quot;CookieUtils should use the original response when saving a cookie&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-5893&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-5893&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; CookieUtils should use the original response when saving a cookie&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fallback to the original response only if the current one is not WebResponse. This way the buffering (BufferedWebResponse) is preserved if possible&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(cherry picked from commit 80e1dbbc49101508d0eae0090fd3aa3d427e3c97)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
